"Degawa Girls Gathering Special."

4
00:00:10,080 --> 00:00:12,560
One day,
we visited Madame at her home.

5
00:00:12,720 --> 00:00:14,440
What will we do this time?

6
00:00:14,560 --> 00:00:17,680
This time, it's the Fourth
Degawa Girls Gathering.

7
00:00:17,760 --> 00:00:19,360
- Degawa Girls Gathering?
- Yes.

8
00:00:20,200 --> 00:00:23,880
Shouldn't it be
Dewi Girls Gathering? Come on.

9
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:25,800
We don't want Tetsuro.

10
00:00:25,880 --> 00:00:28,480
Madame will decide the programme
of the girls gathering.

11
00:00:28,880 --> 00:00:30,960
We can't go abroad now,

12
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:34,480
so if we'll go somewhere in Japan,
it would be Iriomote Island.

13
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:37,440
But the Miyagawa Expedition
has been there.

14
00:00:37,520 --> 00:00:41,040
In the past, Imoto went
to all the places I wanted to go to,

15
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,560
and lately, Daisuke...

16
00:00:43,640 --> 00:00:44,480
Sorry.

17
00:00:45,120 --> 00:00:48,000
They all visit places
I wanted to go to, before me.

18
00:00:48,080 --> 00:00:50,800
But we can do something else,
can't we?

19
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:55,000
So their destination
is Iriomote Island.

20
00:00:55,080 --> 00:00:56,760
Madame said
she wanted to go to Iriomote?

21
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:59,400
She really has a lot of energy.

22
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:03,400
It's impressive for an 81-year-old
to want to go to Iriomote.

23
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:06,880
This time, there's a new Degawa Girl
named Yumena Yanai.

24
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:08,440
What does she look like?

25
00:01:08,520 --> 00:01:09,720
You don't know her?

26
00:01:09,800 --> 00:01:11,240
I've neither seen nor met her.

27
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:14,680
This girl? She looks very healthy.

28
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:20,400
What will their journey be like?
Stay tuned!

